      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I need some help planning my trip to Tokyo next week. I'll be staying in the Marunouchi area but have several meetings scheduled over in Shibuya. Can you help me put together a rough itinerary for a 4-day work week? I mainly need to make sure I account for travel time between the two districts and find some decent, quiet cafes in Shibuya where I can take calls or get some work done between meetings.",
